premise_source_doc_sentence: Avatar premiered in London on , 2009 , and was internationally released on and in the United States and Canada on , to positive critical reviews , with critics highly praising its groundbreaking visual effects .

The film was premiered by 20th Century Fox in London , England on December 10 , and was released in the United States and Canada on December 18 , grossing $ 27 million on its opening day and $ 77 million during its opening weekend in 3,461 theaters , ranking number one at the box office .
